♪We will have our own wedding
in the future♪

129
00:11:05,020 --> 00:11:13,020
♪Will she still twist her body
in the crimson light♪

130
00:11:13,020 --> 00:11:21,340
♪Dancing all you want
with the lake water in the glass♪

131
00:11:21,340 --> 00:11:29,780
♪Crazy and depressed♪

132
00:11:29,780 --> 00:11:38,100
♪The darkening dusk
makes people get sick easily♪

133
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:46,380
♪The heartbroken snow
has begun to melt♪

134
